            "sub_head": "<p>Yes, we offer flexible payment options through Klarna and PayPal Pay in 3. These let you spread the cost of your MacBook repair over time.</p><p>Both options are available at checkout for standard repairs. If you are sending your MacBook in for diagnostics, we will include the payment options with your quote once your MacBook repair plan is confirmed.</p>",
            "alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "accordion",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How do you ensure the quality of your MacBook repairs?",
            "sub_head": "<p>Every MacBook goes through multiple rounds of testing to make sure the repair is done right.</p><p>When a device arrives, we carry out a full intake check before it reaches the repair team. Once the repair begins, we run pre checks to confirm the fault and rule out any secondary issues. After the repair, your MacBook goes through full post repair testing and a final quality check completed by a technician who was not involved in the repair itself.</p><p>We also invest in ongoing training, and our technicians develop solutions for the latest MacBook issues, including faults Apple has not published repair procedures for yet.</p>",
